title: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
headline: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
subtitle: Speed Demon Übermacht Cypher Livery
content:
Thank you for completing any First Dose mission on Hard difficulty in less than 10 minutes between January 12 and February 8. Your gift of the Speed Demon Übermacht Cypher Livery will be available before February 17.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon.
